author: Discovery
description:
Join the Raneys as they help struggling homesteaders transform their spaces into efficient, protected properties. In this compilation of amazing renovations, they set up tilting solar panels for a Colorado family, rebuild a California homestead that was ravaged by fire, and help a war veteran who lost his stable to hurricane-force winds.

Stream Homestead Rescue on discovery+ ► https://www.discoveryplus.com/show/homestead-rescue

#HomesteadRescue #Discovery

About Homestead Rescue:
Marty, Matt and Misty Raney use their building, farming and hunting expertise to help people who strive to live off the grid.
